@page "/about"
<PageTitle>About Us | Pensoft Systems</PageTitle>

<div class="bg-[#0f1c35] text-white py-16 px-6 sm:px-10 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, #f97316 1%, transparent 30%);"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <p class="text-orange-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 text-sm">African Based Company</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">About Us</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-16 lg:py-24 px-6 sm:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

        <div class="max-w-4xl mb-16">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                An innovative software development, IT Services, Engineering and Management Consulting Company domiciled in Kenya. Our innovative methodology and processes constantly deliver improved results for our customers to stay ahead of their competitors. As a professionally managed company, we provide best of breed service to our customers which transform their business.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-orange-500">❖</span> Our Vision
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    The knowledge based solutions provider for the African Region.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-orange-500">❖</span> Our Mission
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Delighting all stakeholders through Solutions in; Software, Engineering, Healthcare and Consulting.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-orange-500">❖</span> Our Plan
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Our Plan is to offer service to improve productivity, reducing operating costs and risk, and optimizing IT infrastructure and processes to ensure optimal performance.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-orange-500 lg:col-span-2 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-orange-500">❖</span> Our Core Values
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Our core values are Integrity, Professionalism, Innovation, Teamwork, Responsiveness, and Competitiveness.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-orange-500">❖</span> Our Clients
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Our client-focused approach ensures that we deliver effective, functional solutions that meet our client's initial aspirations and overall business objectives.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>